description:
&lt;p&gt;Bolton NHS Foundation Trust is seeking to appoint a Practice Education Facilitator to support the Pre-Registration Team&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working as a member of the Clinical &amp; Professional Department based in the Patient safety &amp; experience Directorate, you will be expected to work closely with the Pre - registration team, providing support to professional and education staff thus ensuring the provision of high quality multiprofessional learning environments within Bolton NHS Foundation Trust, and will be required to work locally within services where Interprofessional learning opportunities can be promoted. The post holder will be required to support the breadth of the student experience, which may require cross boundary working, and contribute to the delivery of the new Quality Assurance Concordat.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Team working is essential and the individual should have an adaptable attitude, use their initiative, and have good clinical expertise, excellent interpersonal skills and the ability to work as part of a dynamic team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are essentially looking for someone who has the passion, determination and creativity to support the delivery of results.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you feel you have the skills we would love to hear from you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Previous applicants need not apply.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameSamantha BulpittJob titleLead for Pre-Registration EducationEmail addresssam.bulpitt@boltonft.nhs.ukTelephone number01204 390390 ext 141675&lt;/p&gt;
